  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 2nd Level, when you hit a creature with a melee weapon Attack, you can expend one spell slot to deal radiant damage to the target, in addition to the weapon’s damage.</p><p>The extra damage is 2d8 for a 1st-level spell slot, plus 1d8 for each Spell Level higher than 1st, to a maximum of 5d8.</p><p>The damage increases by 1d8 if the target is an Undead or a fiend, to a maximum of 6d8.</p><p> </p><p><strong>midi-qol:</strong></p><p>This item uses the \"item macro\" feature where the macro that does the rolling is bound to the item to add the extra damage for undead targets</p><p> Update: according to sources (Jeremy Crawford) improved divine smite does not increase the damage done by a divine smite - despite the helper text in improved divine smite.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
